# LOTW replay fixture v1
# Format:
#   frame <count> [buttons...]
# Buttons use these names: up down left right A B start select.
#
# This fixture waits for the title prompt, starts the game, then holds up long
# enough to exercise vertical movement inside the starting house. It stores
# only controller timing, not ROM data or captured frames.
frame 300
frame 12 start
frame 180
frame 360 up
frame 120
